Documentation
=============

PAWS: Bakery is Blender add-on that provides tools to improve your Texture Baking workflow.

Features:
---------

- Automatic Material Setup for Baking
- Batch Baking of High to Low Poly to Atlas Texture and Per-Object
- Color, Roughness, Metalness, Normal, Ambient Oclussion, AORM, Material ID and other maps
- Workflow Helpers
- Optional Anti-Aliasing (Supersampling)
- Missing a Feature? Check the GitHub Page to see what's planned or learn how you can make it happen!



